                     </persName>
                     
                   did make an assault, putting him in corporal fear and danger of his life, and stealing from his person, one pair of mens shoes, value 3 s. one linen shirt, value 2 s. one neckcloth, value 10 d. one cloth coat, value 3 s. a silk handkerchief, value 10 d. and five shillings in money numbered, the property of the said John
            </rs>; and 
               <persName id="t17740112-25-person316">
